snippet.title: Panel De Pon Event '98 | パネルでポン イベント'９８ (Satellaview) - Satellablog ROM dump archive
snippet.description:
I've decided to pad out my Satellaview video recordings with ROMs released on Satellablog that I didn't record video of yet!

Although in most cases I did this because the games were basically identical to retail counterparts, there are a few exceptions. Either way, though, I hope these recordings will help provide support for the BS-X Project and obtaining more ROM dumps.

Panel De Pon Event '98 was put up for download on Satellablog on 4/9/2010:
http://superfamicom.org/blog/2010/04/redumps-because-sometimes-identical-roms-happen-except-for-the-times-they-arent-that-identical/

This redump verifies the previous Event '98 dump. Also, this happens to have been dumped from my own Memory Pack purchases. :)

I recorded an older video on Event '98 before. This video is quite a bit better both in regard to quality and showcasing elements of the game, so I'll probably retire it...
I created this video with the YouTube Video Editor (http://www.youtube.com/editor)
